Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A few days ago, Boli County public security organ 
cracked a serious case on using counterfeit banknotes. Criminal 
(Li Wengang) was arrested and put on record. 
  On the evening of 29 December, Boli County public security 
bureau received a crime report that someone used counterfeit 
banknotes to buy gasoline and to pay for transportation fees. 
Trough investigation by inspectors, Criminal (Li Wengang) was 
captured in less than 10 hours. According to the confession, 
(Li Wengang) is a jobless person from Jixi city. He ganged up 
with two other persons to trade in counterfeit banknotes from 
Guangzhou and travelled to Boli County to purchase over 34,000 
kg of soybeans, thus making more than 60,000 yuan counterfeit 
banknotes flow into society. At present, this case is 
undergoing further investigation. 

